The requirements are "Easy to Navgigate", which relates to the main, login, shipping information and billing information pages.
The website should be easy to navigate so that user can have an easy and enjoyable shopping experience. 

THe next requirement should be a "More Payment Option". This is so users can use any form of credible online payment options
to buy the items they need and so that they are not limited.

The last requirement is the "Shipping Information Safety". This is to provide secuirty in the users shipping and billing information.

